"{\"uid\": \"si.com-college-cincinnati-news-look-multiple-bearcats-competing-in-2024-summer-olympic-games-01j3fsx9ffdr\", \"text\": \"In this story:  CINCINNATI \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\\u00c2\\u00a0The Bearcats have four former athletes participating in the 2024 Paris Olympic Games,\\u00c2\\u00a0plus,\\u00c2\\u00a0two current enrollees!  Jordan Thompson, Annette Echikunwoke, Vanessa Gilles, Chris Borzor, Naquille Harris, and Ramez Diaa are all slated to compete in events running\\u00c2\\u00a0from\\u00c2\\u00a0July 26\\u00c2\\u00a0to\\u00c2\\u00a0August 11.  The opening ceremony takes place on Friday,\\u00c2\\u00a0July 26. Check out more info on the athletes and event times below:  ANNETTE ECHIKUNWOKE - USA (HAMMER THROW)  HAMMER THROW OLYMPIC SCHEDULE\\u00c2  JORDAN THOMPSON - USA (VOLLEYBALL)  TEAM USA VOLLEYBALL POOL A SCHEDULE  VANESSA GILLES - CANADA (SOCCER)  TEAM CANADA GROUP A SCHEDULE\\u00c2  NAQUILLE HARRIS - ST. KITTS & NEVIS (100M Dash)  100m SCHEDULE\\u00c2  CHRIS BORZOR - REPUBLIC OF HAITI (100M Dash)  100m SCHEDULE\\u00c2  RAMEZ DIAA - Dive  10M DIVE SCHEDULE\\u00c2  Subscribe to our\\u00c2YouTube channel\\u00c2\\u00a0on all things Bearcats athletics and Bearcat Blitz on\\u00c2Apple Podcasts\\u00c2\\u00a0and\\u00c2Spotify!  Bookmark Bearcats Talk for the latest news, exclusive interviews, film breakdowns\\u00c2\\u00a0and\\u00c2\\u00a0so much\\u00c2\\u00a0more.  You may also like:  Look: Nasty Nati Roster Finalized Ahead of TBT 2024  Report: Cincinnati Schedules Multi-Team Event As Non-Conference Schedule Starts Finalizing  Cincinnati Forward Dillon Mitchell Dives Into Transfer Decision: 'Just About Being With The Right People'  Watch: Bearcats Gameplay in EA College Football 25  Watch: Cincinnati Bearcats Touchdown in EA Sports College Football 25  Report: Cincinnati Finalizes November Game Date With Georgia Tech  Cincinnati Loses Commitment From Three-Star Local Linebacker Paul Nelson  Cincinnati Football Lands Commitment From 2025 Offensive Tackle Jaha